The paper discusses the Robust Reading Competition, which involves tasks related to text recognition and understanding. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.DL, cs.LG). Additionally, the platform mentioned in the paper involves data management and evaluation, which could also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
